{"word":"G2758 - κενόω - kenóō - ken-o'-o - Make of none effect","slug":"G2758","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κενόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kenóō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ken-o'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make of none effect"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - kenoo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ken-o'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2756\">G2756</a>; to <i>make empty</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>abase</i>, <i>neutralize</i>, <i>falsify:</i> - make (of none effect, of no reputation, void), be in vain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2754\">G2754</a>, <a href=\"#/G2755\">G2755</a>, <a href=\"#/G2756\">G2756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2757\">G2757</a>, <a href=\"#/G2761\">G2761</a>"}]}